  <FileName>k__BackingField: AmericanMasculinityR1
  <Groups>k__BackingField: []
  <DialogueNodes>k__BackingField:
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d5132a37-36f1-4e46-a971-ce07d3999670
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName3
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 75c6f65b-4588-4edc-a312-d97c9fe58fd8
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 1742.4, y: 44}
    <Text>k__BackingField: American universities and college tend to be more liberal
      in nature. A large percentage of students admitted to such institutions lean
      more towards the liberal left, and staff members similarly also share similar
      political beliefs.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 75c6f65b-4588-4edc-a312-d97c9fe58fd8
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName4
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: cdef18b2-de92-431c-a1f5-f5797429c6fd
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 2462.4, y: 44}
    <Text>k__BackingField: As a result, men who enter college or universities tend
      to adopt more liberal values over time. One such values would be the concept
      of hybrid masculinity which encourages more emotional vulnerability and softness
      amongst men
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d4ce026e-1625-41ea-9e6c-7e4dc07edb22
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 5b1d233a-31ea-4b33-85f5-d3ee90c0aab3
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 179.2, y: 64.799995}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'One reason for the evolution of American contemporary
      masculinity is growing income and more people that rise up the social ladder
      can enter universities or colleges '
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 5b1d233a-31ea-4b33-85f5-d3ee90c0aab3
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName2
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: d5132a37-36f1-4e46-a971-ce07d3999670
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 936, y: 64.799995}
    <Text>k__BackingField: The number of undergraduate admissions has been rising
      across the years. Although there are decline for some years, the overall trend
      is still an increase
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 8993946036734938372, guid: 9cb2e257432a2d84380b22a86bed8bd5, type: 3}
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: cdef18b2-de92-431c-a1f5-f5797429c6fd
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName6
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Those who rise to the upper middle income bracket and
        beyond studying in such institutions?
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 8e10d5f6-b5d1-4626-8d6d-f851053c8dbf
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Not sure?
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 47fd3a0a-6847-47fe-9056-2d540eabf519
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 3332, y: 29.6}
    <Text>k__BackingField: What we discussed previously mainly looks at the men from
      the growing middle income class. Hence, who should we look at next?
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 1
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 79462f47-8e45-406c-9684-d092eb6edc9c
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName8
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 605fcf6a-6f7e-4ab5-8a27-f84401ca3cb4
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 4977.6, y: 70.4}
    <Text>k__BackingField: There is a general correlation between wealth and political
      values. Research show that the wealthy tend to support democratic more and
      lean towards liberal values
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: 7761469775469319506, guid: d8e73123fbee7f64697f411872792092, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 8e10d5f6-b5d1-4626-8d6d-f851053c8dbf
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName7
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 79462f47-8e45-406c-9684-d092eb6edc9c
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 4325.6, y: -357.6}
    <Text>k__BackingField: That's right
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6800915032177342135, guid: 97dbcf3c2e2539d489c7150e0fe63bd8, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
